snippet.title: Swift 3.1 Changes and Interesting Highlights
snippet.description:
Swift 3.1 Changes:
https://www.raywenderlich.com/156352/whats-new-in-swift-3-1

Apple recently released the Swift 3.1 language to all of us iOS developers and it's now time to go over some of the highlights of the language.  In this video I'll be going over Nested Generics as well as the new Swift Version Availability syntax check.  

Visit this link for the Stack Implementation code in Swift 3.1
https://www.letsbuildthatapp.com/course_video?id=1422
